annotationA: 60S ribosomal protein L31; Structural constituent of ribosome. It is involved in the biological process described with: mitotic spindle elongation; translation; mitotic spindle organization; Belongs to the eukaryotic ribosomal protein eL31 family
annotationB: Probable elongation factor 1-beta; EF-1-beta and EF-1-delta stimulate the exchange of GDP bound to EF-1-alpha to GTP
